OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FDeserted, dilapidated, and desperate.
OL,8,FToday, the scale of the crisis facing
OL,9,Four struggling high streets is laid
OL,10,Fbare as an investigation by ITV News
OL,11,FCentral reveals more than a third of
OL,12,Fshops in some parts of the Midlands
OL,13,Fare standing empty.
OL,15,FChallenges including the cost of
OL,16,Fliving crisis, high business rates,
OL,17,Fand street crime have all been cited
OL,18,Fas reasons for the number of shuttered
OL,19,Fshops - with some estimates suggesting
OL,20,Four town centres are losing between 30
OL,21,Fand 40 shops every day.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"People haven't got enough money"
OL,8,FSteven Smith is a market stall holder
OL,9,Fin Bolsover in Derbyshire.
OL,11,FIn the 15 years he's been running a
OL,12,Fstall, he told us how he's seen
OL,13,Fbusiness spiral.
OL,15,F"There's not an awful lot for people
OL,16,Fto come here for, really," he said.
OL,18,F"You get regular customers, and
OL,19,Fthey'll come back. But if you're not
OL,20,Fgetting new customers, you're only
OL,21,Fever going to lose money over time.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@ZO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"It's tough, because I don't think
OL,7,Fthere is much that can be done. I
OL,8,Fdon't see that anybody's going to do
OL,9,Fanything.
OL,11,F"People haven't got enough money.
OL,12,FPeople's habits are changing, they're
OL,13,Fusing online more, using supermarkets,
OL,14,Fout of town shopping centres.
OL,16,F"I just don't see what anybody can do
OL,17,Fto turn it around."
OL,19,FIt's a bleak picture - but one echoed
OL,20,Fup and down the country.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
