OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FUnder the Freedom of Information Act,
OL,7,FI asked councils across the Midlands
OL,8,Ffor figures on the number of empty
OL,9,Fshops in their areas.
OL,11,FOf 56 local councils, only 35 were
OL,12,Fable to provide those figures - but
OL,13,Fthey paint a deeply worrying picture.
OL,15,FOf just under 71,000 retail units,
OL,16,Falmost 7,000 are standing empty -
OL,17,Fthat's 9.7%, or around one in every 10
OL,18,Fshops.
OL,20,FAnd in some places, it's much higher.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FRugby in Warwickshire, has a vacancy
OL,7,Frate of around 12% - while East
OL,8,FStaffordshire Borough Council reported
OL,9,Fa rate of 21.2%.
OL,11,FNorth East Derbyshire was similar, at
OL,12,F21.4%.
OL,14,FAnd Bolsover is one of the worst
OL,15,Faffected - it has the highest shop
OL,16,Fvacancy in the Midlands, at more than
OL,17,F36%.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FFor leaders in Bolsover, the challenge
OL,7,Fhas been trying to find new ways to
OL,8,Fbring people in, and keep them coming
OL,9,Fback - including how to spend a #15
OL,10,Fmillion town centre grant awarded by
OL,11,Fthe government.
OL,13,FCllr Tom Munro, the leader for growth
OL,14,Fat Bolsover District Council, said the
OL,15,Fauthority had invested in shop fronts,
OL,16,Fand a Saturday market - and insisted
OL,17,Fthere's more to come.
OL,19,F"We've also encouraged cultural events
OL,20,Fin the town, and that's brought more
OL,21,Fpeople in," he said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"We've also purchased old buildings
OL,7,Fand buildings that are not currently
OL,8,Fin use, and are planning other uses
OL,9,Ffor those."
OL,11,FThat includes the former Co-op
OL,12,Fsupermarket, just around the corner
OL,13,Ffrom Market Square.
OL,15,FHe said the council is now looking
OL,16,Finto converting it to a mixed-use
OL,17,Fbuilding, working alongside the local
OL,18,Fhealth board to introduce health
OL,19,Ffacilities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
