PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FOther parts of the building, he added,
OL,7,Fcould be used for arts and creative
OL,8,Factivities.
OL,10,FThe move towards mixed-use for town
OL,11,Fcentre buildings is being explored by
OL,12,Fa number of councils.
OL,14,FEvesham in Worcestershire has a
OL,15,Fvacancy rate of 12% overall - but its
OL,16,Ftown centre sits in the shadow of the
OL,17,Fcarcass of shops gone by.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
