CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FThe Riverside Centre has been labelled
OL,7,F"Britain's saddest shopping centre" by
OL,8,Fone national newspaper, with only one
OL,9,Fstore - a Home Bargains - still open
OL,10,Fand operating inside.
OL,12,FThe others have all been abandoned.
OL,14,F"Many towns across the country are the
OL,15,Fsame as Evesham - people are driving
OL,16,Fout of them instead of into them," the
OL,17,Fdeputy council leader, Cllr Emma
OL,18,FKearsey, told us.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@cO]vD@AOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"The most time that people probably
OL,7,Fspend in Evesham at the moment, sadly,
OL,8,Fis when they're queuing in traffic to
OL,9,Fgo through it."
OL,11,FBut Wychavon District Council has a
OL,12,Fplan. Earlier this year, it bought the
OL,13,FRiverside Centre - and now has plans
OL,14,Fto raze it to the ground, replacing
OL,15,Fthe empty shop units with a mix of
OL,16,Fhousing, retail, and leisure.
OL,18,FA reflection, she said, of the way
OL,19,Fpeople's habits have changed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
