PN,37311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"What we want to do is for people to
OL,7,Factually come to Evesham, for it to be
OL,8,Fthat destination," she said.
OL,10,F"Years ago we had lots of coaches come
OL,11,Fin, people all come into the
OL,12,FRiverside. And we have thousands and
OL,13,Fthousands of people that come to the
OL,14,FBattle of Evesham event that we have".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@RO]rD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"So we want it to be that what's in
OL,7,Fthe town, is what people want to come
OL,8,Fin for - for their spending habits,
OL,9,Fand what they want to do for leisure,
OL,10,Fso that it's all inside the town. "So
OL,11,Fit brings Evesham back to being a town
OL,12,Fthat you want to go to."
OL,14,FThe decline of the high street is a
OL,15,Fhuge concern for people.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
