FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FFormer Chancellor of the Exchequer
OL,7,FLiam Byrne, who's also the MP for
OL,8,FBirmingham Hodge Hill and Solihull
OL,9,FNorth, has been researching the issues
OL,10,Fwhich voters are most concerned with -
OL,11,Fand empty shops comes up time and time
OL,12,Fagain.
OL,14,F"A lot of people right now think that
OL,15,Factually that communities are in real
OL,16,Fdecline and the barometer of that, if
OL,17,Fyou like, is just the state of the
OL,18,Flocal high street," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"So if you've got shops that are
OL,7,Fshuttered or if you've got fly
OL,8,Ftipping, maybe you've got some
OL,9,Fcommunity facilities there that have
OL,10,Fbeen closed down for a long time, and
OL,11,Fyou don't feel like in any control".
OL,13,F"There's nothing you feel that you can
OL,14,Fdo to change that. And actually that
OL,15,Fmakes you feel that it's not just your
OL,16,Fcommunity - it's the country that's
OL,17,Fgoing backwards."
OL,19,FAs for what can be done to fix it, he
OL,20,Fhas some ideas.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"We need to get really tough on high
OL,7,Fstreet crime"
OL,9,F"Labour costs are going up. Energy
OL,10,Fcosts are going up. Crime costs are
OL,11,Fgoing up. Business rates are going
OL,12,Fback up. The VAT threshold is in the
OL,13,Fwrong place.
OL,15,F"Any one of those things, you could
OL,16,Fprobably handle - but all of those
OL,17,Fthings together, it's just proving too
OL,18,Fmuch for people.
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"And that's why you're seeing shop
OL,7,Funits shutting down all over the
OL,8,Fcountry. High streets are maybe losing
OL,9,Faround 38 shops a day because of this
OL,10,Fcombined pressure that's now on
OL,11,Fthem."It's not like one thing (that's
OL,12,Fneeded).
OL,14,F"There's actually a big package of
OL,15,Fthings, and it probably starts with
OL,16,Fgetting business rates down. Online
OL,17,Fgiants are frankly getting away with
OL,18,Fpaying too little when high streets
OL,19,Fare paying too much.
OL,26,@sD@FOUsD@_pmtD@Gpn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
