SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"We need to get really tough on high
OL,7,Fstreet crime. We've got to bring
OL,8,Fenergy costs down. We've got to give
OL,9,Flocal government more power to
OL,10,Factually work out who owns all of the
OL,11,Fshop units so that they can actually
OL,12,Fdrive through regeneration much more
OL,13,Fambitiously."
