CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,7,FCommunities, Housing, and Local
OL,8,FGovernment said:
OL,10,F"High streets are not just the beating
OL,11,Fheart of our economy, they are at the
OL,12,Fcentre of our communities and that's
OL,13,Fwhy we're backing them and ensuring
OL,14,Fthey can thrive.
OL,16,F"We are investing #300 million to
OL,17,Frevitalise them, introducing powers to
OL,18,Fallow councils to tackle long-term
OL,19,Fvacant properties, and cracking down
OL,20,Fon high street crime with more to come
OL,21,Fthrough our High Streets Strategy."
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G18/28
