OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FSandwell Council is among those
OL,7,Finvesting in making its town centres
OL,8,Fmore appealing. Its spent almost #3m
OL,9,Fof government grant money in
OL,10,FBlackheath widening pavements,
OL,11,Fcreating more crossings, and a new bus
OL,12,Finterchange - while in August last
OL,13,Fyear, it opened its new indoor market
OL,14,Fin West Bromwich, to great fanfare.
OL,16,FOn opening day, queues snaked through
OL,17,Fthe market itself, out the door, and
OL,18,Fdown the street.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G19/28
