OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FOf particular interest was the return
OL,7,Fof iconic Black Country brand Firkins
OL,8,F- bucking the trend and reopening a
OL,9,Fhigh street store after 10 years as an
OL,10,Fonline-only business.
OL,12,FManaging director Rob Green said it
OL,13,Fhad "overwhelmingly" been the right
OL,14,Fdecision."Opening day was
OL,15,Funbelievable. The queue was around the
OL,16,Fblock for three to four weeks after we
OL,17,Fopened, and it continued like that
OL,18,Fright the way through till Christmas,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@TO]vD@JOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G20/28
