FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37321
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"Obviously it's gone back to a normal
OL,7,Flevel now - which is still more than
OL,8,Fwe could have anticipated to start
OL,9,Fwith. "You can't get that connection
OL,10,Fto customers by being online," he
OL,11,Fadded."But times are getting tougher
OL,12,Fon the high street. Everyone's feeling
OL,13,Fthe pinch. "Things are up and down all
OL,14,Fover the place in the economy at the
OL,15,Fmoment. But I'm confident that we're
OL,16,Fin a good place. We're a strong,
OL,17,Fviable business."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GOUrD@^O]sD@GOUuD@LOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G21/28
