OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FAnd some areas have seen success. In
OL,7,FLeicestershire, Oadby and Wigston
OL,8,FBorough Council reports an empty shop
OL,9,Frate of around 9% - slightly below
OL,10,Faverage, according to our figures.
OL,12,FBut on Wigston High Street itself -
OL,13,Fit's the lowest it's been in a decade,
OL,14,Fwith almost no empty shops to be found.
OL,16,FThe council says it's worked hard to
OL,17,Fbring in a variety of businesses to
OL,18,Ffill them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G22/28
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
