CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"People's shopping habits have
OL,7,Fchanged. The town centres are not just
OL,8,Fa place for people to come in to shop
OL,9,Ffor few things and go back," Cllr
OL,10,FSamia Haq, the council leader, said.
OL,11,F"It's actually a whole day out where
OL,12,Fpeople look for entertainment. They
OL,13,Flike to socialise and they like to, at
OL,14,Fthe same time, go to the shops and buy
OL,15,Fwhatever they need.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@\O]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G23/28
