FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37324
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"So we have a good variety of shops
OL,7,Fhere. We have cafes, restaurants, and
OL,8,Fwe have some service providers as
OL,9,Fwell, as well as your traditional
OL,10,Fretailers in the town centre. That
OL,11,Fmakes people spend more time in the
OL,12,Ftown centre - and in turn, it helps
OL,13,Four traders."
OL,15,F"It's the community that makes us so
OL,16,Fgreat"
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@MO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G24/28
