OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,FAmong the businesses to move in is the
OL,7,FPeony Cafe, a Turkish eatery run by
OL,8,FHatice Akta and her children, which
OL,9,Frecently celebrated its first
OL,10,Fanniversary.
OL,12,FHatice's daughter Betul helps out
OL,13,Fbehind the counter, and said it was
OL,14,Fthe community which helped businesses
OL,15,Fin the town thrive.
OL,17,F"When we first opened, my family were
OL,18,Fcomplete strangers to them. But now we
OL,19,Fknow our customers - we know their
OL,20,Fnames, " she said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU|D@HOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G25/28
