PN,37326
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779955502
OL,3,CBritain's 'saddest shopping centre':
OL,4,COne in three shops shut in some areas
OL,6,F"We've seen unimaginable support from
OL,7,Fall the community members here.
OL,8,FThey're all really supportive. They
OL,9,Fknow that my mum opened this cafe as a
OL,10,Fsingle mum. Honestly, it's been
OL,11,Fincredible.
OL,13,F"It's the community that makes us so
OL,14,Fgreat to be in this part of Leicester."
OL,16,FAnd their customers agree.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@gO]
